that check for $10,000.

31:14.046 --> 31:16.483
Good luck, bladesmiths.
We'll see you in four days.

31:16.613 --> 31:19.007
- Good luck.
- Kevin.

31:23.838 --> 31:26.232
- So, it's day one
in Belleville, West Virginia.

31:26.362 --> 31:28.277
I got a spatha to go make.
